OL,3,CWelsh Government announces changes to
OL,4,Ccontroversial farming payment scheme
OL,6,FFarmers in Wales will not be expected
OL,7,Fto have a minimum of 10% tree cover on
OL,8,Ftheir land, after changes to a
OL,9,Fcontroversial subsidy scheme.
OL,11,FHuw Irranca-Davies, the deputy first
OL,12,Fminister of Wales, confirmed a number
OL,13,Fof changes to the Welsh Government's
OL,14,Fcontroversial sustainable farming
OL,15,Fscheme.
