OL,3,CWelsh Government announces changes to
OL,4,Ccontroversial farming payment scheme
OL,6,FThe scheme, which resulted in
OL,7,Fthousands of farmers protesting
OL,8,Foutside the Welsh Parliament in
OL,9,FCardiff Bay in February, was widely
OL,10,Fcriticised by opposition parties and
OL,11,Ffarming leaders.
OL,13,FMr Irranca-Davies said changes to the
OL,14,Fscheme addressed the needs of Welsh
OL,15,Ffarmers while supporting sustainable
OL,16,Fproduction of food, as well as climate
OL,17,Fchange and nature commitments.
