OL,3,CWelsh Government announces changes to
OL,4,Ccontroversial farming payment scheme
OL,6,FSpeaking from the Royal Welsh Winter
OL,7,FFair, he said: "Following the
OL,8,Fconsultation, it was clear changes
OL,9,Fwere needed, we said we would listen
OL,10,Fand we've done just that.
OL,12,F"Farmers are at the heart of
OL,13,Fcommunities right across Wales, and
OL,14,Fthey play a crucial role in our
OL,15,Feconomy and food production.
OL,17,F"As stewards of our land, they also
OL,18,Fhave a key role to play in protecting
OL,19,Fand restoring nature and tackling the
OL,20,Fclimate emergency."
