OL,3,CWelsh Government announces changes to
OL,4,Ccontroversial farming payment scheme
OL,6,FChanges to the scheme include the
OL,7,Fremoval of a farm-level figure for
OL,8,Ftree cover, which will be replaced
OL,9,Fwith a scheme-wide target.
OL,11,FA spokesman said: "Farmers will
OL,12,Ftherefore no longer be asked to have a
OL,13,Fminimum of 10% tree cover on their
OL,14,Fland."
OL,16,FFarmers who apply for the scheme will
OL,17,Fbe able to decide where they want to
OL,18,Fadd more trees or hedges on their farm
OL,19,Fand how many, with funding to support
OL,20,Fthem through the optional part of the
OL,21,Fscheme.
OL,26,@sD@SOUvD@FO]
