OL,3,CWelsh Government announces changes to
OL,4,Ccontroversial farming payment scheme
OL,6,FHowever, farmers will still be
OL,7,Frequired to manage at least 10% of
OL,8,Ftheir farm as habitat.
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government is now
OL,11,Fconsidering options to create
OL,12,Ftemporary habitat to help farmers meet
OL,13,Fthis requirement, which should be
OL,14,Fsuitable for all farming systems and
OL,15,Fland ownership.
OL,17,FActions relating to animal health,
OL,18,Fwelfare and biosecurity have been
OL,19,Fmerged to focus discussions with the
OL,20,Ffarm vet on improved health and
OL,21,Fwelfare outcomes, the spokesman added.
