OL,3,CWelsh Government announces changes to
OL,4,Ccontroversial farming payment scheme
OL,6,FThe scheme had included a requirement
OL,7,Ffor all farms to have wash stations,
OL,8,Fwhere equipment is cleaned, but this
OL,9,Fis now optional.
OL,11,FAdditional payments will be made for
OL,12,Fsocial value under the universal part
OL,13,Fof the scheme, representing the "wider
OL,14,Fbenefits which come from a sustainable
OL,15,Fagricultural industry", the Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment said.
