OL,3,CWelsh Government announces changes to
OL,4,Ccontroversial farming payment scheme
OL,6,FMr Irranca-Davies added that the
OL,7,Fupdates represented "significant
OL,8,Fprogress" but they were not the final
OL,9,Fscheme, with a decision to be made on
OL,10,Fthis next summer.
OL,12,FDetails of payment rates will not be
OL,13,Fprovided until then.
OL,15,F"We are developing a scheme which is
OL,16,Fdesigned to support all farmers in
OL,17,FWales, based on the completion of a
OL,18,Fset of universal actions," he said.
