OL,3,CWelsh Government announces changes to
OL,4,Ccontroversial farming payment scheme
OL,6,F"These actions will be familiar to
OL,7,Ffarmers in Wales, whether beef, dairy,
OL,8,Farable, upland, lowland, extensive or
OL,9,Fintensive. They are actions many of
OL,10,Fthem take on a day-to-day basis."
OL,12,FHe said the scheme would support the
OL,13,F"economic resilience" of farming
OL,14,Fbusinesses, the sustainable production
OL,15,Fof food, as well as climate and nature
OL,16,Fobjectives, and rural communities.
OL,18,F"We've come a long way and there is
OL,19,Fstill more work to do," he added.
