OL,3,CWelsh Government announces changes to
OL,4,Ccontroversial farming payment scheme
OL,6,FNFU Cymru president Aled Jones,
OL,7,Fspeaking at the Royal Welsh Winter
OL,8,FFair, said it welcomed the
OL,9,F"partnership approach" Mr Irranca-
OL,10,FDavies had put in place to listen to
OL,11,Fthe concerns of the farming industry.
OL,13,FThe union has been involved with the
OL,14,Fministerial roundtable and sub-groups.
OL,16,FMr Jones added: "Welsh Government has
OL,17,Fconfirmed this is not the final scheme
OL,18,Fdesign and Welsh ministers have not
OL,19,Fmade any final decisions.
