OL,3,CWelsh Government announces changes to
OL,4,Ccontroversial farming payment scheme
OL,6,F"Securing Welsh Government's
OL,7,Fcommitment to a well-funded, multi-
OL,8,Fannual budget for the scheme that
OL,9,Fmatches the scale of our ambition for
OL,10,Fsustainable growth of the food and
OL,11,Ffarming sector, alongside the delivery
OL,12,Fof key environmental outcomes for
OL,13,Fsociety, is also going to be crucial.
OL,15,F"We have seen the budget for farming
OL,16,Feroded by inflation and subjected to
OL,17,Fin-year cuts. The need to restore and
OL,18,Fenhance the budget cannot be
OL,19,Foverstated."
