OL,3,CWelsh Government announces changes to
OL,4,Ccontroversial farming payment scheme
OL,6,FMr Jones added that there was a "huge
OL,7,Famount of work to be done on many
OL,8,Faspects of the scheme".
OL,10,FPlaid Cymru described the announcement
OL,11,Fas a "positive shift". Llyr Gruffydd
OL,12,FMS said, "Plaid Cymru have been clear
OL,13,Fall along that Welsh Government needed
OL,14,Fto listen to farmers' concerns about
OL,15,Fthe arbitrary one-size-fits-all
OL,16,Fapproach in the Sustainable Farming
OL,17,FScheme. Without a scheme that works
OL,18,Ffor farmers, there will be no
OL,19,Fenvironmental benefits for anyone.
