OL,3,CWelsh Government announces changes to
OL,4,Ccontroversial farming payment scheme
OL,6,F"While we await more detail on the
OL,7,Freduced number of universal actions,
OL,8,Fthe tree and hedgerow opportunity
OL,9,Fplan, and how much the social payment
OL,10,Fwill be - this is a seemingly positive
OL,11,Fshift from the government,
OL,12,Fparticularly on the most contentious
OL,13,Fissues.
OL,15,F"With SFS serving as the primary
OL,16,Fsource of government support for
OL,17,Ffarming in Wales in the future, it's
OL,18,Fcrucial that the Government gets this
OL,19,Fscheme right for a sector that already
OL,20,Ffeels under siege.
