OL,6,F"Moving forward, we need absolute
OL,7,Fclarity from the government on how
OL,8,Fthis scheme will impact the sector and
OL,9,Fwider society. The proposed revised
OL,10,Feconomic impact assessment will now be
OL,11,Fcritical in that respect.
OL,13,F"Whilst the devil will be in the
